version_description: This is the closest chord patterns for this song.
This tab has a more correct and fuller sound. If you play along with the recording this sounds a lot closer than some of the other higher rated tabs.
Every section, including the rap duet, is written out in full.

I relied and made these chords by listening to original music. I don't know if it sounds right to you, but for now it's sounding right for me. About the Strumming, I'm not sure, but I've tried (thats the first time I trying to do a strumming pattern here). You can change anything if you think you need it. I'll appreciate. Music Link: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_RrA-R5VHQs.
Includes correct chords for the bridge and the verses, as well as all instrumental parts, the chords are aligned neatly with the text, melisma is clearly indicated with dashes.
